{"tid":1384664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢鋪真係要屌政府","createTime":"2019-07-30T02:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T03:34:04.000Z","uid":175490,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d32e2f0b487c3650c7d751ae3f2db72cfd3828a3","tid":1384664,"uid":175490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:33:53.000Z","msg":"頭先喺藍田站<br />\n真係好想講 點解林鄭月娥到依家都未撚落台<br />\n雖然一定好多人覺得啲後生仔又搞著返工<br />\n但係個政府搞到咁樣都唔撚識收皮?<br />\n搞咗個幾兩個月嘅政府有冇做到啲乜嘢實質嘅行動？<br />\n叫警察拉人打人叫咗成個鐘都唔識到<br />\n個差館喺隔離咋喎<br />\n白出糧畀你班廢柴 屌<br />\n政府真係on99"},{"pid":"62b2687082e68d41488dc135ec382ab283c1386e","tid":1384664,"uid":175490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:35:21.000Z","msg":"屌!<br />\n落得台未<br />\n換人啦<br />\n唔識管就唔好阻住"},{"pid":"7d1bfefbe8126862a8adb3fc32b76c82eb368166","tid":1384664,"uid":86037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a138b3ce1a65d6cfe0f60499d03adbbe52334a","tid":1384664,"uid":175490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d1bfefbe8126862a8adb3fc32b76c82eb368166","tid":1384664,"uid":86037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:31:59.000Z","msg":"燥"},{"pid":"06493f1ea86ba1148ccb6be90ef6dbdfdb0199e1","tid":1384664,"uid":65390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:32:53.000Z","msg":"有邊舖唔應該屌政府？"},{"pid":"11123f13e6c9072f9ad3d328306f315e48d35a57","tid":1384664,"uid":175490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06493f1ea86ba1148ccb6be90ef6dbdfdb0199e1","tid":1384664,"uid":65390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:32:53.000Z","msg":"有邊舖唔應該屌政府？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:34:04.000Z","msg":"佢屌唔化"}]}